   @{FG shine}------------------
      INSTALLATION
  --------------------@{FG text}


      Put ADoomGUI in directory in which resides the ADoom executable.

   Games:ADoom/            <- directory in which should be
       ADoom                  ADoom, ADoomGUI & Music files
       ADoomGUI
       ADoomGUI.mount
       ADoom_SndSrvr
       MIDI_Instruments
       .doomrc

       DEH/                <- directory with DeHacked scripts
         DMArmy3.DEH
         Fun_2.DEH
         ...

      To select WAD File dir  you have  to edit ADoomGUI tooltypes and
   write <name>=<path>
         name - name of the Doom WAD version (eg. Ultimate Doom) which
                will appear on GUI's cycle button
         path - path to directory where WAD Files resides
                (eg. PROGDIR:WADS/UltimateDoom)
@endnode

